node.title: Man dies after water incident in Wainuiomata
node.description: A man has died after a water incident in Wainuiomata, south of East Harbour Regional Park, this afternoon.
node.content:
["A man has died after a water incident in Wainuiomata, south of East Harbour Regional Park, this afternoon.", "", "
East Harbour Regional Park map. Photo: RNZ / Charlotte Cook
", "Police were called to the scene off Coast Road about 12.15pm.", "Inquiries into the circumstances of the death are ongoing."]
